   var criteria = request.queryParams.category;
   var result = [];
	
   var cat_item = new GlideRecord('sc_cat_item_category');
   if(criteria){
	   cat_item.addQuery('sc_category.sys_name', criteria);
   }
   cat_item.addQuery('sc_cat_item.active', 'true');
   cat_item.addQuery('sc_cat_item.sys_class_name', 'NOT IN', 'sc_cat_item_wizard');
   cat_item.orderBy('sc_cat_item.order');
   cat_item.orderBy('sc_cat_item.name');
   cat_item.query();
   while(cat_item.next()){
        var item = {};
	    item.catalog = criteria;
	    item.title = cat_item.sc_cat_item.name.toString();
	    item.id = cat_item.sc_cat_item.sys_id.toString();
	    item.page = 'sc_cat_item';
	    item.description = cat_item.sc_cat_item.short_description.toString(); 
	    result.push(item);
   }
	
   //search for subItem
	
   return result;

})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/naci/service_catalog_api/getServiceCategoryItems</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/getServiceCategoryItems</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>false</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-12-11 17:52:02</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>01253fd8db438700f59974131f961991</sys_id><sys_mod_count>18</sys_mod_count><sys_name>getServiceCategoryItems</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_01253fd8db438700f59974131f961991</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-12-12 22:13:46</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="Service Catalog REST API">da904d2fdb7ec300f59974131f961956</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl/><http_method>GET</http_method><name>getServiceCategories</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
   var criteria = request.queryParams.category;
   var result = [];
	
   var sc_cat_item = new GlideRecord('sc_category');
   sc_cat_item.addQuery('sc_catalog.sys_name', 'Service Catalog');
   sc_cat_item.addQuery('active', 'true');
   if(criteria != null && criteria != 'all'){
	   sc_cat_item.addQuery('parent.sys_name', criteria);
   }else{
	   sc_cat_item.addQuery('parent.sys_name', '');   
   }
   sc_cat_item.orderBy('title');
   sc_cat_item.query();
   while(sc_cat_item.next()){
		var item = {};
	    var titleStr = sc_cat_item.title.toString();
        if(titleStr == 'Standard Changes' || titleStr == 'Software Solution Services'){
			continue;
		}
	    item.title = titleStr;
		item.id = sc_cat_item.sys_id;
		item.image = sc_cat_item.getDisplayValue('homepage_image');
	    var subItems = [];
	    var sc_cat_subItem = new GlideRecord('sc_category');
	        sc_cat_subItem.addQuery('sc_catalog.sys_name', 'Service Catalog');
	        sc_cat_subItem.addQuery('active', 'true');
	        sc_cat_subItem.addQuery('parent.sys_name', sc_cat_item.title.toString());
	        sc_cat_subItem.orderBy('title');
	        sc_cat_subItem.query();
	    while(sc_cat_subItem.next()){
	         var subItem = {};
			 subItem.title = sc_cat_subItem.title.toString();
			 subItems.push(subItem);
		} 
	    item.subItem = subItems;
	    if(subItems.length > 0){
			item.hasSubItem = 'true';
		}else{
			item.hasSubItem = 'false';
		}
		result.push(item);
   }
	
   return result;
